{"tid":2449484,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想聽下大家有啲咩夢想","createTime":"2021-03-16T16:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T00:41:28.000Z","uid":367597,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"68272738e3af228894f5b8fa6691eb7f740979c6","tid":2449484,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意飲茶，每次飲茶我都可以食好多點心，要斟幾次茶先夠我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我夢想就係每日都飲茶，朝朝早一自然醒，就行落樓下拎位飲茶，茶樓入面唔會有唔衞生嘅廢老，唔會有啲藍屍睇著茶樓播緊cctvb然後鬧年青人係死廢青，電視可能會播緊啲本土劇，會係由後生仔主導嘅電影或者劇集<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，待應可以係啲有鄉音嘅姐姐，但佢哋都係同後生仔同聲同氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲完茶就翻屋企同另一半一齊睇下書練下琴，學下新嘢，到咁上下就去後花園睇下啲蕃茄種成點，然後磨到下晝就陪兩老去食下午茶，再磨下磨下就夜晚，沖完涼hea一陣咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">但我諗係香港應該冇可能會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3dae0f45cf2d8eec21eb4237b451175908bbec59","tid":2449484,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"比我幸福既人都要仆街死"},{"pid":"9bfaa1853f047be76af5ed228c0401ebf3b12796","tid":2449484,"uid":329698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"填詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夕爺是我偶像"},{"pid":"ca43ef52c2d68190fae638c2099e68304a2fbd2f","tid":2449484,"uid":307223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"太空人"},{"pid":"9d2301301908aaffc5d984a24c301e6a177ada03","tid":2449484,"uid":247184,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"睇到支爆既一日，所有紅屍藍屍粉紅屍全部跳樓死"},{"pid":"9a1f7f740473ab861a20305961e92b09aaffd4f9","tid":2449484,"uid":75390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:08:36.000Z","msg":"搵到女朋友 之後結婚"},{"pid":"cd484669047f69fd7ebd500a3f92e834d14a08c5","tid":2449484,"uid":367597,"like":0,"